# Full Stack Application (.NET Web API + React Vite) 

##  Overview
This project provides a production-ready full stack setup:
- **Backend** â†’ .NET Web API with Identity + JWT authentication
- **Frontend** â†’ React (Vite) client application
- **Database** â†’ Microsoft SQL Server
- **Documentation** â†’ Swagger UI enabled

##  Tech Stack
**Frontend:** React + Vite  
**Backend:** .NET Web API  
**Database:** Microsoft SQL Server  
**Authentication:** ASP.NET Identity + JWT  
**API Docs:** Swagger  

## ðŸ“ Project Structure
/Server â†’ .NET Web API Backend
/Client â†’ React (Vite) Frontend

## âœ… Prerequisites
Ensure the following are installed:

- .NET SDK (version you are using, e.g., .NET 8)
  https://dotnet.microsoft.com/

- Node.js LTS (18+ recommended)
  https://nodejs.org/

